title.rendered: Bank Upholstered Stacking Bar Stool  – various heights available

content.rendered:
The Bank Upholstered Bar Stool can be paired with any of our Bank chairs & stools.

Available with a metal stacking frame in Chrome.

Currently only available in Grey fabric as shown.

Held in stock for delivery in 3-4 working days. CRIB 5 Certified. 1 Year guarantee.

Requires basic self assembly. Suitable for 110KG.
